column5: Hey all, I have been thinking of going to the port maitland pier this weekend to try and catch some perch and walleye. Does anyone know if this is a good spot for perch and walleye or not? thanks in advance!  Matt.
good spot for sheephead and maybe smallmouth bass, lots of gobies also. perch don't really come into the pier in the fall as for walleye you might get lucky
